{"tid":2248032,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家用開咩broker 去做交易?","createTime":"2020-10-18T09:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T14:00:00.000Z","uid":344846,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d72f460bed7424a30057cfb669dad813c107cb58","tid":2248032,"uid":344846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"本身用開Interactive broker (IB pro)，但發現好多時每個月要俾錢買data + Platform using fee 好on9。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>富途牛牛</ins></strong><br />\n用過一次之後永遠唔會再用<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>Interactive broker (pro)</strong></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.interactivebrokers.com/en/index.php?f=1590&amp;p=stocks2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.interactivebrokers.com%2Fen%2Findex.php%3Ff%3D1590%26p%3Dstocks2&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1aw%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=ba7a6471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.interactivebrokers.com/en/index.php?f=1590&amp;p=stocks2</a><br />\n如果喺Tier，每一次交易大約喺USD 0.35。每個月你要俾~USD 14.5買real-time data，TWS 每個月都要俾USD 10。你果個月commission 過USD 10，可以waive 走其中USD 10。我自己用緊IB (pro)，覺得佢最好好處有下面幾個: <br />\n1. 佢訂單執行速度喺快(唔知喺咪因為每個月要俾平台費USD 10) <br />\n2. Multi-market exposure(可以用嚟買到全球大部份市場產品)<br />\n3. 借margin 好平<br />\n4. 買美金好平<br />\n<br />\n但喺唔知喺咪開始做得多交易，commission 開始貴、平台使用費、data subscription 令我諗緊: 其他broker 都已經無咗，點解我仲要俾? <br />\n<br />\n所以問下大家用緊咩broker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(有諗過TD Ameritrade，但上網聽聞佢個order execution 速度好慢? )"},{"pid":"dbe387abaf52729876b7b4f66ebbfa6a7f1a67bf","tid":2248032,"uid":55917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"CS"},{"pid":"b87f95cae9f6b96f3707f6b74ea6ea695b6b9154","tid":2248032,"uid":19065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa8384534926cfe0af12855ebc84bab31d57d01","tid":2248032,"uid":344846,"like":0,"dislike":0,